  "detailed_description": "<h1>YOU CAN SUPPORT US</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/b2a510cc55df6feba619cb810038de50.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><br><h1>YOU CAN PARTICIPATE IN DEVELOPMENT</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defense</h2>Enemies attack your hive from time to time. They drop bombs, spray poison and launch rockets. Each time they will become stronger. Build ballistae, machine guns, anti-aircraft missile launchers and other defenses to protect your hive<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/cdb23a942576c59af8b5c3183714ffc2.poster.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/cdb23a942576c59af8b5c3183714ffc2.webm?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/cdb23a942576c59af8b5c3183714ffc2.mp4?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your path</h2>Research new technologies and buildings to keep up with the enemies. Choose which technologies will lead you to victory. Will you end the war with peace or with the destruction of all enemies?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/3cd43e2b9c83b062a6135c362197294c.poster.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/3cd43e2b9c83b062a6135c362197294c.webm?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/3cd43e2b9c83b062a6135c362197294c.mp4?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bees</h2>The queen needs more workers and warriors. Build kindergartens, schools, military bases and grow new bees that will benefit the hive.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/7bd0150101d3dd860a4bae28c1fee27e.poster.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/7bd0150101d3dd860a4bae28c1fee27e.webm?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/7bd0150101d3dd860a4bae28c1fee27e.mp4?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Factories</h2>There are 7 types of resources in the game, and to get some of them you will need factories. Build honeycombs and place buildings on them<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/85a7202ae255c62e3f85a3a320e733ad.poster.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/85a7202ae255c62e3f85a3a320e733ad.webm?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/85a7202ae255c62e3f85a3a320e733ad.mp4?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relaxation</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/6c9a4b4927163f563f1bdd73b964730b.poster.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/6c9a4b4927163f563f1bdd73b964730b.webm?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/6c9a4b4927163f563f1bdd73b964730b.mp4?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defense</h2>Enemies attack your hive from time to time. They drop bombs, spray poison and launch rockets. Each time they will become stronger. Build ballistae, machine guns, anti-aircraft missile launchers and other defenses to protect your hive<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/cdb23a942576c59af8b5c3183714ffc2.poster.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/cdb23a942576c59af8b5c3183714ffc2.webm?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/cdb23a942576c59af8b5c3183714ffc2.mp4?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your path</h2>Research new technologies and buildings to keep up with the enemies. Choose which technologies will lead you to victory. Will you end the war with peace or with the destruction of all enemies?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/3cd43e2b9c83b062a6135c362197294c.poster.avif?t=1773142721\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/3cd43e2b9c83b062a6135c362197294c.webm?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345020/extras/3cd43e2b9c83b062a6135c362197294c.mp4?t=1773142721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bees</h2>The queen needs more workers and warriors. Build kindergartens, schools, military bases and grow new bees that will benefit the hive.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class